      <title>德雷福斯要求 ICE 交易所在糖交付延迟后介入</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/dreyfus-asks-ice-exchange-to-step-in-after-sugar-delivery-delays</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，路易达孚公司 (Louis Dreyfus Co.) 要求洲际交易所 (InterContinental Exchange Inc.) 介入因纽约交易所销售的食糖交货延迟而引发的纠纷。]]></description>
